00:30:24,870 --> 00:30:26,840
直到他肯回家了"
until he feels like coming home?"

489
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:32,110
但是  那小子可真是倔
But man, oh, man, that boy was stubborn.

490
00:30:33,430 --> 00:30:35,440
