And he just shook his head no.

496
00:30:49,270 --> 00:30:51,450
第二天早晨  我醒来  往窗外一看
Well, the next morning, I woke up, I looked out the window

497
00:30:51,450 --> 00:30:53,560
沃特还在树上
and Walter was still up in that tree.

498
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:58,000
于是早饭之后  我拿着一盘鸡蛋过去
So after breakfast, I walked over with a plate of eggs...

499
00:30:58,340 --> 00:31:00,040
问他是否想来点
and I asked him if he wanted some.

500
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:02,150
他又摇头
And again, he just shook his head.

501
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,780
我生气了
And I got angry.

502
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:08,310
那小子有个好房子  好家庭
That boy had a good house, a good family,

503
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:09,850
