And I gave that tree a good whack.

509
00:31:22,940 --> 00:31:25,030
沃特大喊  但我没停手
And Walter cried out, but I kept on.

510
00:31:25,030 --> 00:31:25,770
你从没听过
I mean, you've never heard

511
00:31:25,770 --> 00:31:27,860
我砍树时  沃特发出的
screams like the one coming from Walter

512
00:31:27,860 --> 00:31:29,970
