as I chopped at that tree.

513
00:31:30,710 --> 00:31:31,490
他都尿裤子了
He pissed his pants,

514
00:31:31,490 --> 00:31:33,250
淋了下来
and it came raining down on the ground,

515
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:35,110
但我毫不在乎
but I didn't pay it no mind.

516
00:31:35,540 --> 00:31:37,470
我还继续砍
I just kept whacking away.

517
00:31:39,050 --> 00:31:39,950
于是
Well...

518
00:31:40,150 --> 00:31:41,850
没过多久沃特就下来了
it didn't take long before Walter was on the ground

519
00:31:41,850 --> 00:31:43,470
跑回了自己家
and running back to his house.

520
00:31:43,570 --> 00:31:46,270
